additionalObject.implementation: <!-- Allowed XML root element instances --> <xsd:element name="PLMContainer" type="PLMContainer" />
additionalObject.name: additionalObject2

attribute.implementation: <xsd:element name="PropertyType" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:choice> <xsd:element name="NumericalValue" type="NumericalValue"/> <xsd:element name="CartesianPoint" type="CartesianPoint"/> </xsd:choice>
<xsd:choice> <xsd:element name="ExternalModel" type="ExternalModel"/> <xsd:element name="GeometricModel" type="GeometricModel"/> <xsd:element name="StyledModel" type="StyledModel"/> </xsd:choice>

<xsd:element name="Version" type="PartVersion" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>PartVersion instances are marked as optional (minOccurs = 0), instead of using nillable=true</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> </xsd:element>

entity.name: TranslatableString
entity.implementation: <xsd:complexType name="TranslatableString"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="Translation" type="Translation" minOccurs="0"/></xsd:sequence> <xsd:attribute name="value" type="xsd:string" use="required"/> <xsd:attribute name="lang" type="xsd:language"/> </xsd:complexType>

entity.name: EventOrDate
entity.implementation: <!-- Help types --> <xsd:complexType name="EventOrDate"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>To preserve correct semantics one of the attributes shall be used.</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> <xsd:attribute name="date" type="xsd:dateTime"/> <xsd:attribute name="event" type="xsd:IDREF"/> </xsd:complexType>

entity.name: PeriodOrDate
entity.implementation: <xsd:complexType name="PeriodOrDate"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>To preserve correct semantics one of the attributes shall be used.</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> <xsd:attribute name="Event" type="xsd:IDREF"/> <xsd:attribute name="Date" type="xsd:dateTime"/> <xsd:attribute name="Duration" type="xsd:duration"/> </xsd:complexType>

entity.name: PLMCoreContainer
entity.implementation: <!-- Abstract super types --> <xsd:complexType name="PLMCoreContainer" abstract="true"> <xsd:attribute name="uid" use="required" type="xsd:ID"/> <xsd:attribute name="versionId" use="optional" default="1.0" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:attribute name="lang" use="optional" type="xsd:language"/> </xsd:complexType>

entity.name: PLMObject
entity.implementation: <!-- Base type for all objects --> <xsd:complexType name="PLMObject" abstract="true"> <xsd:attribute name="uid" use="required" type="xsd:ID"/> </xsd:complexType>

entity.name: PLMRootObject
entity.implementation: <!-- Base type for root elements - objects that can be instantiated inside Container --> <xsd:complexType name="PLMRootObject" abstract="true"> <xsd:complexContent> <xsd:extension base="PLMObject"/> </xsd:complexContent> </xsd:complexType>

entity.name: referencesInfo
entity.implementation: <!-- Information types --> <xsd:complexType name="referencesInfo" xmlns="urn:bo_model/schemaInfo"> <xsd:sequence/> <xsd:attribute name="name" use="required" type="xsd:QName"/> </xsd:complexType>
